Puzzle Boy
==========

Yet another puzzle boy (a.k.a Kwirk http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kwirk) clone.
Website: http://code.google.com/p/puzzleboy/

This is the SDL2/OpenGL version, which is in beta stage.

